  "texts": [
    "By integrating AI into their workflows, organizations can significantly strengthen their overall security posture and proactively safeguard their sensitive assets.",
    "e-ISSN: 2582-5208 International Research Journal of Modernization in Engineering Technology and Science ( Peer-Reviewed, Open Access, Fully Refereed International Journal) Volume:04/Issue:12//December -2022 Impact Factor-7.868 www.irjmets.com www.irjmets.com @International Research Journal of Modernization in Engineering, Technology and Science [2160]• Sophos' intercept X-Sophos' Intercept X tool showcases the remarkable utilization of artificial intelligence (AI) in the domain of cyber security.",
    "This sophisticated solution harnesses deep learning neural networks, meticulously modeled after the intricacies of the human brain, to accurately differentiate between harmless and malicious files.",
    "Intercept X boasts the ability to analyze an extensive array of file features, conducting thorough assessments and swiftly determining the safety or potential hazards within milliseconds.The system's training is reinforced by real-world feedback and two-way threat intelligence, resulting in exceptional precision in detecting both existing malware and zero-day threats.",
    "Furthermore, Intercept X maintains an impressively low false-positive rate, mitigating the risk of erroneously flagging benign files as malicious.This compelling case study underscores the immense potential of AI in fortifying defensive measures against the constantly evolving landscape of cyber threats."
